snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4297 | 17 Jan 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4297: Bapuji's Rescue
--------------------------------------------------------
As Bapuji's bluff is exposed by the Pakistani soldiers, he faces a difficult challenge. Will he manage to rescue both himself and the fishermen from this predicament?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4297 | 17 Jan 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000305430

snippet.title: EGG BONDA | MUTTAI BONDA | Road Side Evening Snacks Recipe Cooking In Village | Bajji Street Food
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring you the ultimate recipe for Egg Bonda (Muttai Bonda), a beloved roadside evening snack that everyone enjoys! Watch as we prepare this crispy, golden-brown delight in a traditional village setting, using fresh ingredients and time-honored cooking techniques.

The Egg Bonda is made by coating perfectly boiled eggs with a spiced gram flour batter and frying them to perfection. This mouthwatering snack is best enjoyed hot, with an evening. Whether you're a fan of street food or looking for a quick and tasty recipe to try at home, this video has you covered!

Get a glimpse of authentic village-style cooking and join us as we prepare this classic Indian snack in a scenic, peaceful atmosphere.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

Will it be Team Blue or Team Red that impresses the judges and takes home the victory? 🏆 Watch as the teams bring their A-game, face hilarious kitchen disasters, and surprise us with their culinary skills!

snippet.title: 8th Pay Commission Updates: 8वें वेतन आयोग से कितनी बढ़ेगी सैलरी? समझिए पूरा कैलकुलेशन
snippet.description:
8th Pay Commission Updates: 8वां वेतन आयोग किस तारीख से लागू होगा, इसे लेकर अभी ऐलान नहीं किया गया है, लेकिन परंपरागत तौर पर वेतन आयोग का गठन हर 10 साल में किया जाता है. जिसमें केंद्रीय कर्मचारियों की सैलरी, भत्ते और लाभों की समीक्षा की जाती है और कोई सुझाव या बदलाव होते हैं तो उसके लिए प्रस्ताव दिए जाते हैं.

Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche


Baade rooh de rangeen Munde 
Att de shaukeen Munde 
Gaal hove ankhan di
Saade bad scene hunde
Sire de ae dith
Tappe saadi leek
Fer malo mali malo mali malo mali
Sir  chad jaande parche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche
Obvious ae gaal saade hone charche
Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Tu beeta hua kal
Mera flow jaise Future 
Underground chalu jaise mein
Mewat ka koi Buchter
Jo bars meri week thi 
Vo tere liye tutor hai 
Tu ankh band kre baitha jaise koi kabootar hai
 Gangster sune mere gaane baithe jail mein
Mein Dm Nahi krta bars karu mail mein
Naam k hi rapper hai yeah sun tu detail mein
Labelo pe dekhe hai zameer inke sale mein
Luck te nahi khade hai hukk the
Mein Fuck na deyu Koi deta jo takht pe
Vakht hai mera inki jamante japt hai
Mere doore Dhari inki amante girvi
Inke pale daale kuch ni 
Yeah baat maare fir bhi
Jind k julane tak
Delhi k buwane tak
Naam le diye tu tanne pahochade tikane tak
Maa duae mere sath hai sath hai 
Oh sikra mein guddi kya baat hai baat hai
Bhai kisse ka digaya nahi digda mein
Jab tak sar pr bhole ka mere hath hai hath hai
Ehna hoya ni siyana 
Har cheez te mein bola
Kaam di ae bukh fame da ni rola
Buss dekhi chalo jatt kidda thal de barola
Jurta naa jande ae takh palte
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

snippet.title: Saif Ali Khan Attack Case: Watch Moments After Attack On Actor, Kareena Seen Outside Residence
snippet.description:
Bollywood actor Saif Ali Khan’s team has issued a statement following reports of an attempted burglary at his residence and an alleged stabbing. Saif Ali Khan’s maid has also been stabbed in the attack. Police has recorded the maid's statement and the CCTV footage is under examination. Four individuals have been detained in connection with the case. Watch the full video on Times Now.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS |  Real Madrid 5-2 Celta de Vigo | Copa del Rey 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid made it through to the quarter-finals of the Copa del Rey, overcoming Celta in a hard-fought match that was settled in extra time thanks to Endrick’s brace and another from Valverde. Earlier, our team had taken a 2-0 lead after a stunning finish from Mbappé and another from Vini Jr. However, the Galicians equalised in the final minutes through Bamba and Marcos Alonso from the penalty spot. On January 20th, Ancelotti's side will learn who their opponent will be in the next round of the competition.
#LaCopaMola

es.title: RESUMEN | Real Madrid 5-2 Celta de Vigo | Copa del Rey 2024/25
es.description:
El Real Madrid logró el pase a los cuartos de final de la Copa del Rey. Venció al Celta en un partido muy disputado que se resolvió en la prórroga gracias a un doblete de Endrick y a otro gol de Valverde. Antes, nuestro equipo se había puesto por delante 2-0 tras un gran tanto de Mbappé y otro de Vini Jr. Sin embargo, los gallegos igualaron el encuentro en los minutos finales por medio de Bamba y Marcos Alonso, de penalti. El 20 de enero los de Ancelotti conocerán a su rival en la siguiente ronda de la competición.
#LaCopaMola

snippet.title: America Wildfires: अमेरिका में तबाही और आग के फैलने की पूरी कहानी (BBC Hindi)
snippet.description:
#israel #hamas  #californiafire 

बीबीसी दुनिया में आज देखिए - 

* ग़ज़ा में जारी हैं इसराइली हमले
* इमरान ख़ान को भ्रष्टाचार मामले में 14 साल की सज़ा
* आग पर क़ाबू पाने की कोशिशें जारी 
* रूस में नवेलनी के वकीलों को जेल 

प्रोड्यूसर- विदित मेहरा, अदिति, अरशद

* ऐसे ही और वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

* बीबीसी हिंदी से आप इन सोशल मीडिया चैनल्स पर भी जुड़ सकते हैं-

snippet.title: Hyundai Creta Electric Drive Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Hyundai is finally launching its new EV, made in India for the Indian market. It will be available in two battery packs and various trims and is expected to start at around Rs 17 Lakh. The top end with 51.4Kwh and ADAS features should cost more than Rs 22 Lakh. I got a chance to drive it recently, and here are my impressions.

00:28 Charging
02:01 Exteriors including Key fob, Wheels, Charging port, etc

20:45 Rear seat space and amenities
22:30 Boot Space
23:30 Drive Impressions on City & Highway roads, including Ride, Dynamics, Handling, Power, ADAS, Regeneration, etc.
36:16 Conclusion

snippet.description:
Kerala Blasters'  pursuit for playoffs received a huge boost after a last-gasp win over Odisha FC.


The hosts fell behind early, but surged back before eventually Noah Sadaoui's stoppage-time winner downed Odisha FC 3-2. Jesus Jimenez and Kwame Peprah were the other goal-scorers for the hosts, while Jerry Mawihmingthanga and Dorielton found the back of the net for the Kalinga Warriors.

snippet.title: Bhide ने Jetha को सिखाया ज़िम्मेदारी का पाठ |Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah|Jetha-Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Daya purposefully loses the Antakshari so that everyone can sleep, and Jethalal orders dinner for everyone because they all appear to be hungry. She makes Champaklal and Jethalal proud with this gesture. Later, all of the locals get together at Sodi's house to organize the Gokuldham Society's anniversary.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 199
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Jetha Aur Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTAUo34hpXVbh1keqAyhuhj

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

MAHAVATAR NARSIMHA Hindi hits theaters worldwide on April 3rd, 2025.

When Faith is Challenged, He Appears.
In a World torn apart by Darkness and Chaos... 
Witness the Appearance of the most Ferocious, The Half-Man, Half-Lion Avatar-Lord Vishnu's Most Powerful Incarnation.

Unleash the Fury! Witness the Roar of Mahavatar Narsimha

Mahavatar Narasimha is an epic that brings to life the legendary tale of Lord Narasimha,

snippet.title: First Computer to QUANTUM COMPUTERS - Full Technology Evolution Explained
snippet.description:
Checkout LPU to learn new age skills - https://shorturl.at/VdcQ8 

Research references -  https://docs.google.com/document/d/1FS4NCssJYfQtDOlTsFr1FsLU6dV-D44JCmuwYWOl31k/edit?usp=drivesdk

The fastest supercomputer, El-Capitan, costing ₹5,000 crores, performs 2 quintillion calculations per second. However, it’s about to be surpassed. Google’s Quantum AI Chip "Willow" can process calculations 1 Nonillion (1 followed by 30 zeroes) times faster than today’s supercomputers. Tasks requiring 500 trillion times the universe's age for completion on current supercomputers can now be done in just 5 minutes. This breakthrough marks the beginning of a quantum computing revolution.
Quantum computing could unlock solutions to the universe’s deepest mysteries, pinpoint alien life, enable light-speed travel, cure all diseases, extend human life to 150-200 years, and even achieve immortality by uploading consciousness into machines.
However, creating quantum computers as accessible as today’s systems remains a challenge. Companies like Microsoft, Amazon, IBM, and Intel are working to solve this, but Google’s innovation puts it ahead in the race. This technology is poised to transform the impossible into reality.

snippet.title: Vikrant ने अनजाने मे Mannat की मदद की | Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Sneak Peek | Colors TV
snippet.description:
📲 Download JioCinema: https://bit.ly/3Be09Z3

Accepting the truth of her parentage, Mannat visits the hospital and assures her mother that she will continue to love her, even though she is not her biological mother.

Vikrant ने अनजाने मे Mannat की मदद की | Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Sneak Peek | Colors TV

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannat’s biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shruti’s life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannat’s rising career, Shruti’s failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?


Main Cast and Their Characters:
Ayesha Singh as Mannat
Adnan Khan(Vikrant
Mona Vasu as Aishwarya
Sharain Khanduja as Mallika
Mamta Verma as Shruti
Delnaaz Irani as Harneet
Hasan Zaidi as Gagan

Rushad Rana as Rony

snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: Saif Ali Khan Attack के बाद हाउसहेल्प ने क्या बताया, बिल्डिंग के बारे में बड़ी बात पता लगी। Kareena
snippet.description:
Bollywood actor Saif Ali Khan was attacked with a knife around 2 am. After which he was admitted to Lilavati Hospital. At present Saif's condition is stable. After the attack on Saif Ali Khan, the police is also interrogating the people working at his house. The police suspect the house help, on the basis of which the interrogation is being done.

snippet.description:
#ayngaran  #kamalhaasan #ilaiyaraaja 

Mahanadhi (transl. The Great River) is a 1994 Indian Tamil-language crime drama film directed by Santhana Bharathi and co-written by Kamal Haasan. The film stars Haasan and Sukanya, with S. N. Lakshmi, Tulasi, Shobana, Dinesh, Poornam Viswanathan, Rajesh and V. M. C. Haneefa in supporting roles. It revolves around a widower and his family going through many miseries due to the machinations of a con artist.

Song credits :

Lyrics : Vaali
